des:
American Humor skill has endless american phrases and slang words. American Humor is here to entertain you with one american phrase at a time. American Humor will tickle your funny bone with its humorous attitude and fun facts. 

American Humor skill is a fun skill which gives you common american phrases and slang words. Alexa and American Humor are a perfect match to liven up your living space with fun and humor. 

You invoke the skill by saying "Alexa, open american humor" or "Alexa, ask american humor". You can ask American Humor for an american phrase or a slang word. 

"Alexa, open american humor and tell me an american phrase" 
"Alexa, open american humor and give me an american phrase" 
"Alexa, open american humor and give me a slang word" 
"Alexa, ask american humor and give me something" 
"Alexa, ask american humor for an american phrase."

Alexa will respond with an american phrase or a slang word with its meaning and explanation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
